	"document_notes": [
		{
			"text": "Security update for slurm_20_11",
			"title": "Topic",
			"type": "Summary"
		},
		{
			"text": "This update for slurm_20_11 fixes the following issues:\n\n- Udpate to 20.11.7:\n- CVE-2021-31215: remote code execution as SlurmUser because of a PrologSlurmctld or EpilogSlurmctld script leads to environment mishandling (bsc#1186024)\n- Ship REST API version and auth plugins with slurmrestd.\n- Add YAML support for REST API to build (bsc#1185603).\n- Fix Provides:/Conflicts: for libnss_slurm (bsc#1180700).\n",
			"title": "Details",
			"type": "General"
		},
